RandomTarget (script event)
===========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns a random targeted entity.

Usage
-----

*entity* randomTarget( *string* ignoreName )

Parameters
----------

-   [ignoreName] - The name of an entity to ignore.

